            <description><![CDATA[应该不会就我一个人觉得每个颜色都很好看吧<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>【44.8】La Chapelle+/拉夏贝尔 复古老爹鞋 <br> <br>它们应该是在搞清仓清库存，就怕它随时就无了，喜欢的姐妹可以赶紧捡个漏，反正它还送运险<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[偷笑]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_touxiao-0d995330b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>有三个颜色可选，都是很百搭的配色，码数从35-40都有<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>，它还带点小增高，穿着也不会累脚，毕竟它家原价还是得要上几百大洋滴，一分钱一分货，质量还是可以信赖滴🆗<img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2mg1r8j20j60j640y.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2myc3oj20j60j6di5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2ngm77j20j60j6gnr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2nzzqcj20j60j6ac0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2oicxaj20b40b8q3g.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gzqx2p29vjj20eg0ef75d.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
